FT  10 AUG 94 / Scharping attacks Kohl at election rally
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Rudolph Scharping, who is challenging Helmut Kohl to take over as German
chancellor, addresses supporters in Bonn yesterday after opening the final
phase of his election campaign.
